title: Navigate forwards to a slider
setupScriptDescription: sets focus on a link before the Red slider
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate forwards from here' link, navigate to the 'Red' slider.

title: Navigate backwards to a slider
setupScriptDescription: sets focus on a link after the Red slider
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate backwards from here' link, navigate to the 'Red' slider.

title: Request information about a slider
instructions: With focus on the 'Red' slider, request information about the slider.

title: Increment a slider by one step
instructions: With focus on the 'Red' slider, increase its value one step to 129.

title: Decrement a slider by one step
instructions: With focus on the 'Red' slider, decrease its value one step to 127.

title: Increment a slider by ten steps
instructions: With focus on the 'Red' slider, increase its value 10 steps to 138.

title: Decrement a slider by ten steps
instructions: With focus on the 'Red' slider, decrease its value 10 steps to 118.

title: Decrement a slider to the minimum value
instructions: With focus on the 'Red' slider, decrease its value to its minimum of 0.

title: Increment a slider to the maximum value
instructions: With focus on the 'Red' slider, increase its value to its maximum of 255.
